cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.DL 

This paper discusses data exploration and visualization systems, which are related to database systems (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions challenges related to scalability, which is a common concern in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and systems and infrastructure (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses systems developed by the Semantic Web community, which is related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DL).
